(firstQuint)Oral Carvedilol in Escalating Doses in the Acute Treatment of Atrial Fibrillation.

 Patients with AF with FVR of any etiology were evaluated and given escalating doses of oral carvedilol in doses - 3.

125mg OD, then 3.

125 bid, then 6.

25mg bid, then 12.

5mg bid.

 The ECG was recorded regularly and analysed for rate reduction or control.

